data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT [rfq_id] ,[rfq_erp_no] ,[rfq_title] ,ISNULL(c_count, 0) c_count ,ISNULL(sp_count, 0) sp_count ,ISNULL(sb_count, 0) sb_count ,[rfq_description] ,[rfq_deadline] ,[rfq_grade] ,[rfq_filename] ,[rfq_size_kb] ,[rfq_status] ,[rfq_type] ,CASE WHEN rfq_type=1 THEN 'Standard' WHEN rfq_type=2 THEN 'Single Sourc' ELSE 'Unknown' END AS r_type ,[rfq_approveuser] ,[rfq_approvedate] ,[rfq_posted] ,[rfq_posteduser] ,[rfq_modified] ,[rfq_modifieduser] ,(SELECT STUFF((SELECT ', ' + cat.category_name FROM app_rfq_maps rmp LEFT JOIN app_categories cat ON rmp.rmap_category=cat.category_id WHERE rmp.rmap_rfq=rfq_id FOR XML PATH('')) ,1,1,'') AS Txt) AS r_categories FROM [app_rfqs] r LEFT JOIN (SELECT rmap_rfq, COUNT(*) c_count FROM app_rfq_maps GROUP BY rmap_rfq) c ON r.rfq_id=c.rmap_rfq LEFT JOIN (SELECT submission_rfq, COUNT(*) sb_count FROM app_submissions WHERE submission_supplier != -1 GROUP BY submission_rfq) sb ON r.rfq_id=sb.submission_rfq LEFT JOIN (SELECT rmap_rfq, COUNT(*) sp_count FROM (SELECT DISTINCT rmap_rfq, rmap_category, smap_supplier FROM app_rfq_maps rm LEFT JOIN app_supplier_maps sm ON rm.rmap_category=sm.smap_category ) spn GROUP BY rmap_rfq ) sp ON r.rfq_id=sp.rmap_rfq WHERE rfq_id=@rfqId

data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value: SELECT prd.ROWID, 0 AS PRICE,0 AS QUANTITY, prd.ROWID,prd.PSHNUM_0,prd.PSHFCY_0,prd.ITMREF_0,prd.ITMDES1_0,prd.ITMDES_0,QTYPUU_0,PUU_0, prd.CUR_0,LINAMT_0,prd.CREUSR_0,prd.CREDAT_0 ,submission_rfq ,submission_posted ,[sprod_id] ,[sprod_submission] ,[sprod_erp_id] ,[sprod_code] ,[sprod_quantity] ,[sprod_cost] ,ROUND([sprod_quantity] * [sprod_cost], 2) s_amount ,[sprod_comments] ,[sprod_status] ,[sprod_createuser] ,[sprod_createdate] ,u.Username sd, [Full Names] supplier_name ,u.[Postal Address] ,u.Email ,u.[Contact Number] ,u.Country FROM [app_submission_products] p LEFT JOIN [192.168.105.198\SAGESQL].[x3data].[CIDRZTEST].[PREQUISD] prd ON p.[sprod_erp_id]=prd.ROWID LEFT JOIN [app_submissions] s ON s.submission_id=p.sprod_submission LEFT JOIN app_users u ON u.ID=s.submission_supplier WHERE sprod_status=8 AND [sprod_submission] IN (SELECT [submission_id] FROM [app_submissions] WHERE [submission_rfq]=@srfq)
